Use the standard library

This is how to is_palindrome of text:
   Remember that n is text's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that ok is 1
   Do this quotient of n and 2 times:
      When item i in text is not item (diff of (diff of n and 1) and i) in text, then:
         Remember that ok is 0
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is ok
Now you know

>>> is_palindrome of ""
1
>>> is_palindrome of "aba"
1
>>> is_palindrome of "aaaaa"
1